-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107050328/https://www.theverge.com/platform/amp/2019/10/10/20908117/dyson-electric-car-ev-project|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Dyson axes electric car plan|url=https://www.carmagazine.co.uk/amp/car-news/tech/dyson-plots-electric-car-with-breakthrough-battery-car-june-2016/|access-date=2021-05-19|website=CAR Magazine|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605180348/https://www.carmagazine.co.uk/amp/car-news/tech/dyson-plots-electric-car-with-breakthrough-battery-car-june-2016/|archive-date=2020-06-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>）。
